node.text: We are thrilled to finally share the story and inspiration behind our @katemarkerhome textiles and celebrate the official launch of this new line! As I reflect on the process of turning my daughters watercolor motifs into a textile line with the help of my friend @ellishaalexina and my wonderful team, I am hopeful that these fabrics will bring love, joy, and warmth into your home. I can't thank you all enough for your continued support throughout throughout this launch. All textiles are now available to be purchased as pillow covers or fabric by the yard @katemarkerhome. Produced by @margaretrajic and Shot by @courtneycimo

node.text: Through the use of warm woods, soft pastels and airy finishings, the guest room is the ideal oasis away for visitors to escape from the hustle and bustle. #goodasgoldclient #kmidesignstyle | photo: @stofferphotographyinteriors | build: @grandtraditionhomes | architect: @momentdesign_architecture

node.text: Create a pantry that’s equally as functional and easy on the eyes as the rest of your kitchen. Hide your snacks in style! 😉 #beautifulinsideandoutclient #kmidesignstyle | photo: @margaretrajic | build: @warmanconstruction

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kate Marker Interiors on July 27, 2021. May be an image of living room.

node.text: Putting the finishing touches on each room is the cherry on top. Wall art, shelf decor, and desktop accessories are the final touches that help pull everything together. #brickbybrickclient #kmidesignstyle | photo: @stofferphotographyinteriors | build: @tartanbuilders
